data.description: Fantastic 2 Level, 4 Bedroom Home in Manassas Park. Home is spacious and well maintained perfect for any family. Home also has a driveway and a detached garage with extra storage. Home features upgrades that have applied in the past 5 Years. The bathrooms has been renovated in 2022. The Roof of the home has been replaced in 2022.  Also the Garage roof has been replaced in 2019. Home is within walking distance to parks, schools, and the community center in the area. Seller is offering $750 credit towards the carpet. Home is AS-IS condition and Seller Rentback is needed.
